# UI, i18n, and Accessibility

- Reuse existing shadcn/ui primitives from `src/components/ui/*`.
- Match existing visual style and spacing conventions in nearby pages.
- Use `cn(...)` helper for conditional class composition.

## i18n

- Use `useTranslation()` and `t('...')` for user-facing strings.
- Avoid introducing new hardcoded UI text when translation keys exist.

## Accessibility

- Keep semantic labels connected to inputs via `htmlFor`/`id`.
- Use `aria-invalid` for invalid form inputs.
- Preserve keyboard accessibility of dialogs, menus, and buttons.
